I can say I'm castrated too.

293
00:20:18,150 --> 00:20:20,141
你怎么知道我是不是呀，你说吧
Can you prove I'm not?

294
00:20:21,086 --> 00:20:24,021
我屁股生疮，我屁股有两个洞
I can say anything.

295
00:20:24,089 --> 00:20:26,990
有三个肚脐，谁知道呀？
Like I have 3 belly buttons, who can tell.

296
00:20:27,059 --> 00:20:28,083
除了不可以生孩子外
As long as you keep your clothes on.

297
00:20:28,160 --> 00:20:29,149
