Go now, or we'll have you executed.

1185
01:20:57,118 --> 01:20:58,176
我真的是太监呀
I am a eunuch.

1186
01:20:58,286 --> 01:21:00,117
好
Alright.

1187
01:21:11,166 --> 01:21:13,100
你带几个人上车搜查
Search the coach.

1188
01:21:13,201 --> 01:21:14,190
跟我来
Follow me.

1189
01:21:14,269 --> 01:21:16,100
是
Yes.

1190
