站着
Stand still.

1191
01:21:25,013 --> 01:21:26,173
举起双手
Hands up.

1192
01:21:31,152 --> 01:21:32,210
走吧
Go.

1193
01:21:33,255 --> 01:21:34,187
别动
Don't move.

1194
01:21:34,289 --> 01:21:36,052
走吧
Go.

1195
01:21:39,060 --> 01:21:40,220
你，起来
You, stand up.

1196
01:21:40,996 --> 01:21:42,088
从那里来的？    山东
- Where are you from? - Shantung.

1197
01:21:42,163 --> 01:21:43,187
不用怕    山东？
- It's alright. - Shantung?

1198
